        <p>
		a. <gap dim="left" extent="unknown" reason="lost"/> Ioannes <gap dim="right" extent="unknown" reason="lost"/></p><p>b. <gap dim="left" extent="unknown" reason="lost"/> <seg cert="low">renewing</seg> <gap dim="right" extent="unknown" reason="lost"/></p>
      </div>

      <div type="commentary">
        <head>Commentary</head>
		<p>See discussion at <xref type="eAla-text" n="IV.37">IV.37</xref>.</p>
      </div>

